001package io.cyborgcode.roa.api.annotations;
002
003import java.lang.annotation.ElementType;
004import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
005import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
006import java.lang.annotation.Target;
007
008/**
009 * Container annotation that allows multiple {@link ApiHook} annotations
010 * to be applied to a test class.
011 *
012 * <p>This annotation is used internally by Java‚Äôs repeatable annotation mechanism;
013 * you normally use {@code @ApiHook} directly.
014 *
015 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
016 */
017@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
018@Target(ElementType.TYPE)
019public @interface ApiHooks {
020
021   /**
022    * The wrapped array of {@link ApiHook} annotations.
023    *
024    * @return one or more ApiHook annotations
025    */
026   ApiHook[] value() default {};
027
028}
